{
  "stem": "3097.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I had a very good education, and I received a so-called matura, a certificate of maturity, which allowed you to go to a-- higher-- for higher education, you see.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] for university.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, because of the climate.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You see, you could-- there were, in my town, there were two public high schools.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But you couldn't get in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Or maybe, out of the whole population, maybe one or two students were accepted.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was a very strict, closed number where you could get in.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "For example, all high schools in Poland were under supervision of the government, of the area-- educational area and so forth.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So there was always a supervisor, and when you had the examination, did terminal examination, there was a delegate from Krakow-- we belong to Krakow-- who came and checked us and-- and wrote our certificates.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was also a Hebrew education.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Although the-- the spoken and written word was Polish, but there you could also have a matura, or maturity examination, in Hebrew language, and Hebrew literature.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was exempt from it, because I could not-- because I came to the second class already, I didn't have the background to keep up, so I was relieved.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was a Professor [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Mayevski, ?] who constantly talked to me, because I sit in the class.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He says, Zelinger, why don't you try to do that, you see?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You're missing so much.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The-- the man was such an idealist.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I-- in part, I didn't pay any more attention, in part I knew it would be more difficult for me.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because I had already difficulties, at that time, to pick up with other boys, because they were bright kids there, you know.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were very, very smart kids.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
